  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Security To protect Personal Information from unauthorized access and use we use security measures that comply with applicable federal and state laws These measures may include device safeguards and secured files and buildings as well as oversight of our third party service providers to ensure information remains confidential and secure Please visit bankofamerica com/security for additional information</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

